  "question": "Do AMR determinants, plasmid Inc-types, and (E. coli) virulence genes co-occur / impute each other, within organism? (which resistance rides which plasmid backbone / virulence context)",
  "substrate": "AMR determinants (AMRFinder) + plasmid Inc-replicons (PlasmidFinder) + virulence genes (VirulenceFinder, E. coli) blastn local sweeps over Enterobacterales cohort genomes",
